d5e7dad74bf868a7d7e97f79b1734caf (08:01): i'd love to study chinese
7e4d3980d65af002eede675ea28547a2 (08:02): Chinese is fascinating, yes, but when compared with an alphabetic language.... it's ridiculously time consuming to learn.
7e4d3980d65af002eede675ea28547a2 (08:02): Chinese grammar is, conversely, quite simple.
d5e7dad74bf868a7d7e97f79b1734caf (08:02): but in the end, when China rules America, Chinese will be very useful
7e4d3980d65af002eede675ea28547a2 (08:03): which is why I am taking Chinese!
d5e7dad74bf868a7d7e97f79b1734caf (08:03): I plan to learn it soon haha
d5e7dad74bf868a7d7e97f79b1734caf (08:03): I'm betting that Arabic & Chinese will be very useful in the future
d5e7dad74bf868a7d7e97f79b1734caf (08:04): as will not being american, but I can't change that haha
7e4d3980d65af002eede675ea28547a2 (08:04): yeah. I'm concerned about the perception of America and its citizens...
7e4d3980d65af002eede675ea28547a2 (08:04): Which I find disturbing and almsot unwarranted at times...

7e4d3980d65af002eede675ea28547a2 (08:07): The largest imperialist power the world has ever seen (in my opinion).
The English rant and rave about how despicable America and Americans are... Yet, look at some of the ramifications of English imperialism: the Israeli-Palestinian conflict, the Opium wars, division in the middle east...
7e4d3980d65af002eede675ea28547a2 (08:07): mostly I'm looking at the crisis in Israel/Palestine.
7e4d3980d65af002eede675ea28547a2 (08:08): Britain handled it terribly come post-WWII...
7e4d3980d65af002eede675ea28547a2 (08:08): so, my point is, we're not the only "bad" country out there.
7e4d3980d65af002eede675ea28547a2 (08:08): (though I am unimpressed with a lot of the stuff we have done / do!)
d5e7dad74bf868a7d7e97f79b1734caf (08:08): we are however, very young
d5e7dad74bf868a7d7e97f79b1734caf (08:08): it's like an older brother (UK) teasing us for our mistakes, when he's made plenty himself
7e4d3980d65af002eede675ea28547a2 (08:09): I attribute a lot of it to divisiveness caused by nationalism
7e4d3980d65af002eede675ea28547a2 (08:10): in most other countries around the world there is a very acute and strong sense of national and/or cultural identity...
